    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Using NestedModules is usually the recommended route, yeah. Ultimately any DLL imported will affect the entire PowerShell session regardless of where it's imported, so you can also just use `Import-Module` or `Add-Type` to import the module DLL from a PSM1 if you need that for some reason. ðŸ™‚ ",
